message.content: cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.ME, cs.ET - The paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for automated design of soft robots and their controllers, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). It also mentions the use of simulation and sim2real transfer, which are common topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the design and construction of soft robots, which falls under the category of mechanical engineering (cs.ME) and electronics (cs.ET).
